parameters: Hehe... Ahaha...! Is that story really true... hehe...!

It's all true, you know...! I'm here without even
understanding why...

Phew...! But I'm glad. If those black girls were really bad
people, Laura might have become a serious criminal by now.

That's right. Maybe those girls in black uniforms
infiltrated here to help someone named Cat escape from
prison. Depending on how you look at it, Laura could also be
seen as an accomplice.

Accomplice...? Jailbreak...? Huh... So, Cat-san got caught
in a trap as a treasure hunter...?

That's probably a lie. There probably aren't any classical
traps like that in the underground of Ulyssean.... If it's a
trap in a different sense, then it might be true, though.
Um... so... who saved me when I fell into the lake...?

It's to avoid exposing the infiltration route. You see, if
Laura were to tell the soldiers about the existence of the
underground passage afterwards, it would become unusable,
right?

Um... so... um... The girl who saved me was wearing the same
uniform as Luna... Does that mean she's a student from the
Magic Academy...?

It's not necessarily the case. This uniform can be worn by
those who have certain qualifications. It's possible that
she has already graduated.

(Because not many people know about it, there are also
discounts for students. That's another reason.)

Um... why did I suddenly end up looking like a bad person
and causing a commotion with the soldiers at the end...?

They probably did it to make you look like the victim. If
they thought about it efficiently, it would be best to make
it seem like Laura is the mastermind and use that
opportunity to escape.
Why are you in a place like this?
I was forcibly brought here as a hostage by that woman!!
...Haha! No... I can't help but laugh...!!
That's so mean! I'm really bothered by it!!

H-Hey! That's why... it's good to have kind and bad people
around.

A-And besides, isn't it lucky that you managed to avoid
becoming a criminal with just one night of observation...?

Ugh... But in the end, Lunaroa's identification was also
successfully completed, so I can leave here tomorrow,
right...?
W-What's the point of my futile efforts...?

It might be true... B-but, I was really... h-happy that you
came all the way here to see me, you know?

L-Look... You understood the situation and it was resolved
in just one night. We can leave together... Matching
outfits Matching outfits

Ugh...!! Don't comfort someone like me...! You don't have
the right! Just call me foolish instead...!!
Ahaha... It seems like you're enduring quite a lot.

...But it's true that I felt lonely by myself. And then,
Laura, you flew all the way here. I couldn't help but laugh
a little, but I was really... happy.
So, don't get down anymore... Come over here?

You know, while Lunaroa was at school, I was waiting all
this time... And then the village ended up like that...

When I thought that Lunaroa, who I finally got to meet, had
disappeared... I... I can't take it anymore...! I have to do
something...! My head is filled with thoughts...
Yeah... It was tough, wasn't it...

But... even if something like that were to happen... Luna
would be able to defeat everyone by herself, right?

Hehe... If I were alone... I might have fallen into
despair... But now, because you're here...

...It seems like there's only one bed here. Laura, you must
be tired too. Shall we rest for a bit...?
